\c 2
\s URuthe ukhothoza emasimini kaBhowazi
\p
\v 1 Njalo uNawomi wayelesihlobo somkakhe\x + 3.2. Zaga 7.4.\x*, umuntu oliqhawe onothileyo owosendo lukaElimeleki, lebizo lakhe lalinguBhowazi\x + 4.21.\x*.
\v 2 URuthe umMowabikazi wasesithi kuNawomi: Ake ngiye emasimini, ngiyekhothoza okwezikhwebu ngemva kwalowo engizathola umusa emehlweni akhe\x + Dute. 24.19.\x*. Wasesithi kuye: Hamba, ndodakazi yami.
\v 3 Wasehamba wafika wakhothoza ensimini ngemva kwabavuni. Waqabuka efika kungxenye yensimu kaBhowazi owayengowosendo lukaElimeleki.
\p
\v 4 Khangela-ke, uBhowazi wafika evela eBhethelehema, wasesithi kubavuni: IN\nd kosi\nd* ibe lani\x + Hlab. 129.7,8.\x*. Basebesithi kuye: IN\nd kosi\nd* ikubusise.
\v 5 UBhowazi wasesithi encekwini yakhe eyayibekwe phezu kwabavuni: Le yintombi kabani?
\v 6 Inceku eyayibekwe phezu kwabavuni yasiphendula yathi: Yintombi umMowabikazi eyabuya loNawomi evela elizweni lakoMowabi\x + 1.10,22.\x*.
\v 7 Yasisithi: Ake ngikhothoze ngibuthe phakathi kwezithungo ngemva kwabavuni. Ngakho ifikile, iqhubekile kusukela ekuseni kuze kube khathesi; lokuhlala kwayo endlini kuncinyane.
\v 8 UBhowazi wasesithi kuRuthe: Kawuzwa yini, ndodakazi yami? Ungayikhothoza kwenye insimu, futhi ungedluli usuke lapha, kodwa unamathele lapha emantombazaneni ami.
\v 9 Amehlo akho kawabe sensimini ayivunayo, uwalandele. Angithi ngiwalayile amajaha ukuthi angakuthinti. Nxa usuwomile uye ezimbizeni, unathe kulokhu amajaha akukhileyo.
\v 10 Khona wathi mbo ngobuso\x + 1 Sam. 25.23,41.\x* bakhe wakhothamela emhlabathini, wathi kuye: Ngitholelani umusa emehlweni akho ukuthi unginanze lokhu ngingowezizweni?
\v 11 UBhowazi wasephendula wathi kuye: Kutshengisiwe lokutshengiswa kimi konke owakwenzela unyokozala emva kokufa kwendoda yakho\x + 1.14,16,17.\x*, ukuthi utshiye uyihlo lonyoko lelizwe lokuzalwa kwakho, weza ebantwini owawungabazi ngaphambili.
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* kayiwuvuze umsebenzi wakho\x + 1 Sam. 24.19.\x*, sengathi umvuzo wakho opheleleyo kawuvele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, oze ngaphansi kwempiko zayo ukuphephela\x + Hlab. 17.8; 36.7; 57.1; 61.4; 63.7; 91.4.\x*.
\v 13 Wasesithi: Ake ngithole umusa emehlweni akho\x + Ruthe 2.2,10. Gen. 33.15.\x*, nkosi yami, ngoba ungiduduzile, njalo ngoba ukhulume enhliziyweni yencekukazi yakho, lanxa mina ngingenjengenye yencekukazi zakho\x + 1 Sam. 25.41.\x*.
\v 14 UBhowazi wathi kuye: Ngesikhathi sokudla sondela lapha, udle okwesinkwa, utshebe ucezu lwakho kuviniga\x + Nani 6.3. Hlab. 69.21.\x*. Ngakho wahlala eceleni kwabavuni, wasemkhangeza amabele akhanzingiweyo; wadla wasutha\x + 2.18.\x* watshiya.
\v 15 Kwathi esukuma ukukhothoza, uBhowazi walaya amajaha akhe esithi: Myekeleni ukuthi akhothoze laphakathi kwezithungo, lingamyangisi,
\v 16 laye limhwatshele-ke ngabomu okunye ezinyandeni, likutshiye ukuze akukhothoze, lingamkhuzi.
\v 17 Wakhothoza-ke ensimini kwaze kwahlwa. Wabhula lokho ayekukhothozile, kwaba phose yi-efa\x + Eks. 16.36.\x* \w yebhali\w**.
\p
\v 18 Wakuthwala wangena emzini, loninazala wabona akukhothozileyo; wakhupha wamnika akutshiya esesuthi\x + 2.14.\x*.
\v 19 Uninazala wasesithi kuye: Ubukhothoza ngaphi lamuhla? Usebenze ngaphi? Kabusiswe lowo okunanzeleleyo\x + 2.10.\x*. Wasemtshela uninazala ukuthi usebenze kobani, wathi: Ibizo lalowomuntu engisebenze kuye lamuhla nguBhowazi.
\v 20 UNawomi wasesithi kumalokazana wakhe: Kabusiswe yiN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Gen. 14.19. Hlu. 17.2. Ruthe 3.10. 1 Sam. 15.13; 23.21; 26.25. 2 Sam. 2.5. Hlab. 115.15. Jobe 29.13.\x* engayekelanga umusa wayo kwabaphilayo lakwabafileyo\x + 1.8.\x*. UNawomi wathi kuye: Lowomuntu uyisihlobo sethu esiseduze kithi, ongomunye wabahlengi bethu.
\v 21 URuthe umMowabikazi wasesithi: Ngoba laye uthe kimi: Uzanamathela emajaheni\x + 2.8.\x* engilawo aze aqede sonke isivuno engilaso.
\v 22 UNawomi wasesithi kuRuthe umalokazana wakhe: Kuhle, ndodakazi yami, ukuthi uphume lamantombazana\x + 2.8.\x* akhe, hlezi bakuhlangabeze kwenye insimu.
\v 23 Wasenamathela emantombazaneni kaBhowazi, ekhothoza kwaze kwaphela isivuno \w sebhali\w** lesivuno sengqoloyi. Wasehlala loninazala.